sentences.english: I was always able to figure out more or less where he was.
sentences.chinese: 我总能多多少少地找到他在哪里。

sentences.english: She can more or less assume his cocksureness.
sentences.chinese: 母鸡可以多多少少地装出公鸡的自信。

sentences.english: Again, more or less a sub-category of "appeal" and "overlapping action".
sentences.chinese: 这个，多多少少是吸引力和交迭动作的子原理。

sentences.english: That’s actually the more or less free-market solution.
sentences.chinese: 这多多少少就是实际上的自由市场的解决方法。

sentences.english: Every one of them can be helpful in one way or another.
sentences.chinese: 每一种方法多多少少的都会有帮助。

sentences.english: We can believe his story to a certain degree.
sentences.chinese: 对他的故事我们多多少少可相信一点。

sentences.english: Crimes of violence and attacks on the person require more or less pluck .
sentences.chinese: 造谣惑众和人身攻击是多多少少需要有一些勇气的。

sentences.english: Nearly all species have some ability to detect light.
sentences.chinese: 几乎所有物种多多少少都拥有感知光的能力。

sentences.english: They're located more or less where my body is.
sentences.chinese: 他们多多少少坐落在我的身体。
